    {
        "text": "Stir to mix.",
        "start": 25.284,
        "duration": 2.233
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, add the hot water to the sugar ",
        "start": 30.524,
        "duration": 2.879
    },
    {
        "text": "and make the syrup.",
        "start": 33.403,
        "duration": 2.763
    },
    {
